query: INSERT INTO course_enrollments (userId, bundleId, enrollmentType, paymentStatus, amountPaid, status, progress) SELECT DISTINCT e.userId, 1, 'bundle', 'completed', 99900, 'enrolled', 0 FROM course_enrollments e WHERE e.courseId IS NOT NULL AND e.userId NOT IN (SELECT userId FROM course_enrollments WHERE bundleId IS NOT NULL);
